		<!-- message -->
		<div id="post_message_1311268">
                  
                  Hello fellow sorcerers<br />
<br />
I am a lvl 50 sorcerer in a PVP guild, a DE with superior CV and 8 APW pieces of gear (500 sdf, and most crit/damage rating gear). Also have melee evasion belt/two earrings i swap for pvp<br />
<br />
As the situation stands now, our DPS in PVP is very nerfed compared to melee classes, because of the 40% (or so) damage cap that one can do in one hit.<br />
<br />
It might seem like a lot, but for those of you that PVP, its nothing. When PVPing well geared melee players, Sorcerer hardly stand a chance. First because of resists, you seem to hit partial resists all the time, with CV hitting for 800-900 damage every cast till you die or run.<br />
<br />
Second, their range damage usually hits for 1200, and up to 2000 for monks and rangers. Three 40 range hits (with GU4 they can hit you high in the air too now) and you die, healers cant react to that much incoming DPS at all.<br />
<br />
Finally, its the MACROs that are KILLING US as a class. I have been ONE SHOOTED by monks/rogues plenty of times now to realize how easy it is for them to exploit 40% damage cap, while the sorcerers have no way around but to push char/cv, hoping for char burning damage to make a difference (its nothing now with resists)<br />
<br />
Accumulating all my PVP experience, i have to say that Sorcerers now are the WEAKEST in PVP class, because in GU4 Psionisists got their spells upgrades so its is MOSTLY DOT TYPE spells, thus allowing them to avoid the stupid 40% damage cap.<br />
<br />
Why give us CV when it is broken in PVP??? Why give druids/psionists/necros HUGE DOTS that do HUGE damage within a few seconds? <br />
<br />
Sorcerer PVP DPS is VERY CAPPED, it needs a major boost compared to 3 other caster classes. Figure something out devs please, this situation is very lame. Nerf macro classes so their burst DPS isnt so insane (monks/rogues can one shot every time), nerf resists because our snare/root NEVER EVER LANDS on a lvl 50. I think i had it land on lvl 50s 4 or 5 times total, and being resisted 100+ times i have tried to cast it. It landed on buffless poorly gears people too as well, while the rest just ran on.<br />
<br />
Also, when druids can snare/root almost every time in PVP? Why they have 3 pets that PERMAbash you so you cant even evac, those 3 pets also have 100+ radius attack range, making you get off the horse and enter combat mode?<br />
<br />
PLease give us:<br />
<br />
1. Double spell hit ability (like rogues have) when your spell is immediately casted again for same damage, overriding 40% damage cap<br />
<br />
2. Split CV in half or in three parts (1 hit now and 1 hit second after), and make it stack so it works in PVP!!!!<br />
<br />
3. Give us like 3-4-5 sec dots or something, those huge nukes are worthless ATM<br />
<br />
4. GIve us wards!!! why do clerics have over 10 wards plus different DAs when they can be hitting you for full damage and you are wasting your time hitting ward #7 dying to a cleric dot.<br />
<br />
5. GIve us damage rune for at least same abount of mana/ or hitpoints, trust me, that amount of damage is NOTHING in PVP. Make it work with CV feedback too!!!<br />
<br />
6. Give us an INSTA evac spell castable every hour. We are sooo weak we need it badly.<br />
<br />
7. Give us some ability to negate/mitigate/avoid range spear/shuriken/darts etc damage. THEy hit for damage cap most of the time, hitting HARDER THAN OUR NUKES. i mean, wtf is that, dying in 3 ranged hits to a war or dk or rogue   or monk or SHAMAN!!! please do something, range weapons are hurting us tooo much.<br />
<br />
FInally, just keep in mind that our big pve nukes are WORTHLESS in PVP, we lose to every class, even druids and psionists now too, cause of their big 3-5 sec dots. I hope situation gets better, its so stupid playing the weakest in PVP class right now.<br />
<br />
6.
                  
		</div>
